Multi Elevator Design System
(For simplicity lets consider we have two elevator controlled from same buttons )

Actors
User
System


User Stories
- Users can call the elevator to go up or down
- Users can see the direction & destination of moving elevator from any floor [ In some cases we can hide the destination ]
- Users can enter multiple destinations, after stepping inside the elevator
- Users can see the travel destinations on the screen
- Users can open/close gates on any floor or apply emergency brakes on or in-between any floor


Elevator System Stories
- It should open and close the doors at each destination at predefined intervals
- It should warn the Users when elevator is overweight to step down
- It should stop immediately when the doors are open abruptly while moving ( or slow down & move to the nearest floor and then stop their )
- It shoudl apply emergency brakes when their is a powercut
